@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dgxqik(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.75
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.78)))
    v0 = ((0.52 - (v1 + 0.36 + v2 + 0.05)) / v0)
    tmp = (0.15 - wp.sin(0.18))
    v1 = (wp.abs(tmp) + ((tmp + 0.76 * v1 + 0.34) * v1))
    data[tid] = v0
